author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Texton Property Fund ‍Sees Widely Flat Trend Across All Sectors In Tenant Demand In UK
text:
March 5 (Reuters) - Texton Property Fund Ltd:
* HY ‍NET ASSET VALUE 891.49 CENTS, DOWN 8.8%​​ * ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND OF 47.95 CENTS PER SHARE FOR SIX MONTHS ENDED 31 DECEMBER 2017​
* HY ‍REVENUE R303.2 MILLION, UP 1.0%​ * IN UK ‍SEEING WIDELY FLAT TREND ACROSS ALL SECTORS IN TENANT DEMAND
* IN UK RETAIL SECTOR CONTINUES TO STRUGGLE IN TERMS OF BOTH RENTAL GROWTH EXPECTATIONS AND CAPITAL VALUE​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
